.env*

# Infrastructure inventory (generated files — contain IPs and service info)
data/infrastructure/inventory.json
data/infrastructure/inventory.md

# Credentials
config/google_analytics_credentials.json

# WhatsApp interface (session data + deps)
interfaces/whatsapp/.wwebjs_auth/
